<html lang="zh-Hant" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Neumi 樂享系統 | 細胞級吸收，自動化創富</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-900 text-white font-sans">

    <header class="relative py-24 px-6 text-center bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-950 to-slate-900 border-b border-indigo-800">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-300 to-amber-500">
            Neumi 樂享系統
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            30 秒的日常習慣，透過 HydraStat™ 奈米技術，讓營養直達細胞，開啟您的精準保養時代。
        </p>
        <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/~makto2019" class="bg-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-400 text-slate-900 font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-full text-lg shadow-lg shadow-yellow-500/30 transition-all hover:scale-105">
            立即領取系統諮詢
        </a>
    </header>

    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-16">為什麼選擇 Neumi？</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            {[ {title: "奈米級吸收", desc: "突破傳統極限，真正進入細胞層次。"}, 
               {title: "效率極大化", desc: "臨床驗證的 HydraStat™ 技術。"}, 
               {title: "簡單易複製", desc: "無痛入門，開啟自動化循環。"} ].map(item => (
                <div class="bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-yellow-500 transition-colors">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-3">{item.title}</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
            ))}
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white text-slate-900 py-20 px-6 rounded-t-[3rem]">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-8">AI 自動化行銷助力</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-12">
                我們不僅提供頂級產品，更結合 **AI 自動化銷售系統**。不必再當傳統推銷員，讓數據為您自動跟進、成交，打造真正的被動收入事業。
            </p>
            <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-indigo-100">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-900">Line ID: makto2019</p>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">點擊下方按鈕，加入我們專業團隊</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>